cilium-operator-aws completion 
 Generate the autocompletion script for the specified shell 
 Synopsis 
 Generate the autocompletion script for cilium-operator-aws for the specified shell.
See each sub-command's help for details on how to use the generated script. 
 Options 
   -h, --help   help for completion
 
 SEE ALSO 
 
 cilium-operator-aws 	 - Run cilium-operator-aws 
 cilium-operator-aws completion bash 	 - Generate the autocompletion script for bash 
 cilium-operator-aws completion fish 	 - Generate the autocompletion script for fish 
 cilium-operator-aws completion powershell 	 - Generate the autocompletion script for powershell 
 cilium-operator-aws completion zsh 	 - Generate the autocompletion script for zsh
